    • Constructor Detail

      • Population

        public Population(Fitter[] fitters,
                  int size,
                  int maxDepth,
                  int startingDepth)
        Creates a new population of programs which may be operated on with the given Fitters to determine fitness. Programs are created by running NodeFactory.generateFull(science_fair_genetics.Node, int) and NodeFactory.generateGrow(science_fair_genetics.Node, int) in equal parts for each depth between startingDepth and maxDepth.
        Parameters:
        fitters - An array with fitters to evaluate the generated programs with.
        size - The amount of programs to generate.
        maxDepth - The maximum depth of the @{link Node} tree.
        startingDepth - The initial maximum depth used when generating programs.
